x10.lang

Class Acc

  • x10.lang.Acc
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Accumulator

    abstract public class Acc
    Base calss for Accumulator[T] that has all the methods but without the type parameter T. Instead we perform casts at runtime. We use this class because we do not have existentials in X10 (e.g., when we do not know T such as in ArrayList[Acc].
